              <div className="space-y-4 text-sm">
                <div className="pb-3 border-b border-red-400/30">
                  <strong className="text-base">Silkworm Disease Outbreaks</strong>
                  <div className="mt-2 opacity-90">
                    <em>Risk:</em> Disease can devastate entire batches, reducing yields by 30-50%
                  </div>
                  <div className="mt-2 text-green-400">
                    <strong>Mitigation:</strong> KALRO partnership for disease-free eggs; strict biosecurity protocols; quarantine systems; insurance for major losses; diversified farmer base
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div className="pb-3 border-b border-red-400/30">
                  <strong className="text-base">Climate Variability</strong>
